                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The crystalline ooze is hidden via crystallization, and a creature attempts to forage or mine it</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The crystalline ooze melts into sludge that covers the creature. The triggering creature becomes @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 1} and takes a –5-foot circumstance penalty to its Speeds for 1 hour or until the sludge is removed. The ooze gains a +2 circumstance bonus to checks to Grab creatures covered in sludge. The triggering creature or allies adjacent to it can remove the sludge with a total of 3 Interact actions. These actions don't need to be consecutive or made by the same creature.</p>"
                },
